# =============================================================================
# Replay harness bundles (development-only; see docs/PRP-ADDENDUM-replay-harness.md)
# Rich bundles contain raw audio (.wav) and screen-ROI video — must never be committed.
# Stripped bundles intended as test fixtures live under tools/Moza.ScLink.Replay.Tests/Fixtures/
# and are tracked normally; the ignore below excludes only the recordings directory.
# =============================================================================
tools/recordings/
tools/Moza.ScLink.Replay/bin/
tools/Moza.ScLink.Replay/obj/
tools/Moza.ScLink.Replay.Tests/bin/
tools/Moza.ScLink.Replay.Tests/obj/

